          "id": 1,
          "question": "<p><a name=\"336699\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The relational algebra expression equivalent to the tuple calculus expression</p>\n\n<p>\\( \\{t\\mid&nbsp;t ​ \\in&nbsp;​ r \\land&nbsp;(t[A]=10 \\land&nbsp;t[B]=20)\\} \\) is</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Databases: NIELIT 2016 MAR Scientist B</b></p>",
          "type": "single",
          "options": [
            "<p>\\( \\sigma_{(A=10\\:\\lor\\:B=20)}(r) \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( \\sigma_{(A=10)}(r)\\cup\\sigma_{(B=20)}(r) \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( \\sigma_{(A=10)}(r)\\cap\\sigma_{(B=20)}(r) \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( \\sigma_{(A=10)}(r)-\\sigma_{(B=20)}(r) \\)</p>"
          ],
          "correct_answer": "<p>\\( \\sigma_{(A=10)}(r)\\cap\\sigma_{(B=20)}(r) \\)</p>",
          "marks": 1,
