        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "question": "<p><a name=\"336416\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>If \\( R \\) is a relation in Relational Data Model and \\( A_1,A_2,\\dots&nbsp;A_n \\) are the attributes of relation \\( R \\), what is the cardinality of \\( R \\) expressed in terms of domain of attributes?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Databases: NIELIT 2017 July Scientist B (IT)</b></p>",
